# Dockerfile-specific ignore file for docker/Dockerfile.serving. Patterns are
# still evaluated relative to the build context root (parent of vllm-omni,
# vllm-reka, and moonvalley_ai). Ignore everything at the context root except
# those three sibling repos, then strip common junk inside them.

*

!vllm-omni/
!vllm-omni/**
!vllm-reka/
!vllm-reka/**
!moonvalley_ai/
!moonvalley_ai/**

# Repo hygiene
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes
**/.github
**/.dockerignore
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.tox
**/__pycache__
**/*.egg-info
**/.venv
**/venv
**/.cache
**/.DS_Store
**/.idea
**/.vscode
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo

# Build artifacts
**/build
**/dist
**/node_modules

# Model weights — do not bake into image layers
**/*.safetensors
**/*.ckpt
**/*.bin
**/*.pt
**/*.pth
**/*.onnx
**/*.gguf

# Large media
**/*.mp4
**/*.mkv
**/*.mov
**/*.webm
**/*.wav
**/*.flac
**/*.mp3
